- **Engineering rules**: `docs/ai/CURSOR_RULES.md` (create this for your project)
- **UI/UX Style Guide**: `ui/STYLE_GUIDE.md` and `ui/DESIGN_TOKENS.md`
- **Code Templates**: `code-templates/` - Component, hook, store templates
